description: A vegetarian frittata that is lightly seasoned and has extra texture of the plant based chicken.
name: Frittata with Plant Based 'Chicken' & Cheddar Cheese Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 medium white onion, peeled and diced
200g plant based 'chicken', cut into bite size chunks

recipeInstructions.text: Heat up a 9 inch skillet or similar oven proof pan to a medium heat and then fry the onions and plant based chicken in the chilli oil for 10 minutes.
In a mixing bowl, lightly beat the eggs with the milk and add the salt and pepper.
Pour the egg mixture into the skillet and mix well with the onion and plant based chicken.
Allow the eggs to cook on the skillet for 5 minutes and then cover with grated cheddar cheese and place in the oven for 10 minutes.
Once the edges and top start to brown, remove from the oven and allow to set for 3 minutes before serving.
